dct_title_s: Shinkyō-shō Kanshuku-shō nijūgomanbun no ichi zu
dct_description_sm: Map of Xinjiang and Gansu based on 1919 India Survey Bureau maps.
Relief shown by form lines and spot heights.
Shows major roads, water courses, cities and towns.
